Title: Comment on 'Another form of the Klein-Gordon equation'
Authors: A. Aste (U. of Basel)
Comments: Latex, 4 pages, to appear in Phys.Lett.A
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. A290 (2001) 106
\\
  It is shown that the alternative Klein-Gordon equation with positive definite
probability density proposed in a letter by M.D. Kostin does not meet the
requirements of relativistic (quantum) field theory and therefore does not
allow for a meaningful physical interpretation.
